Requied packages:
libnfnetlink-dev
libnfnetlink0
libnetfilter-queue-dev
libnetfilter-queue1

Recommended packages:
iptables
gzip

Suggeste packages if building on a desktop machine:
dbus
libdbus-1-3
libdbus-1-3-dev

How to build:
git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
make install

If you just want certain modules like just pgld do the above but before "make install"
cd pgl/pgld
Then "make install"


Currently this only builds pgld.

Options to cmake: (syntax: "cmake OPTIONS ..")

-DNODUBS=1
    No DBus support (Auto-detect otherwise)

-DLOWMEM
    Enable LOWMEM support for devices like routers etc
    This disables DBus
